    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_ABD1384B-03BA-4CE3-B865-6FA41A1E2F76" class="text-block-content">
    <p>As an admin, you can manage the colors of the standard gradebook statuses and create custom gradebook statuses for all accounts associated with your account.</p>
<p>Custom statuses are supported in Gradebook imports and SIS exports. Custom Final Grade Override statuses are supported in Gradebook exports.</p>
<p>When a missing label is manually applied, the missing label is removed by a new submission or manual removal. Entering a score does not remove a manually-applied missing label.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-account" data-step-uuid="C595935F-4A83-4009-9FF2-D9F46A37C12F">
    <h2 id="open-account" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Account</h2>
